[07:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'or washed out, so I need to do some color correction. And this is not a Premiere Pro tutorial, so I will go through it very quickly. So, first of all, what I do is that I go here to window workspaces and I do some color correction quickly.'

[07:51] [scene:talk]
